title: Kirsty van der Voort
text: love how pretty the orders are packaged and the extra gifts! such a nice touch, as a customer this makes you definitely feel valued and more likely to order again! prices are a little bit on the high side for some items, but the sale is good value as well and i've seen lower prices on Topvintage than on others so it really depends
